Jurgen Klopp confirmed in a press conference he is to leave Borussia Dortmund this summer . 
  The German will officially leave the club on June 30 after seven years in charge . 
  Klopp has been linked with a move to the Premier League . 
  The 47-year-old said he believed Dortmund needed a change . 
  Manchester City and Arsenal are among the clubs linked with Klopp . 
 